## Install a ton of great apps using Homebrew cask instead of downloading, clicking and manually installing :)

## Standard app replacements
# Web
cask install google-chrome
# Terminal
cask install iterm2

## Boxes
# Virtualization
cask install vagrant
cask install virtualbox
# Containers
cask install boot2docker

## Coding
# SourceTree
cask install sourcetree
# Text editing
cask install sublime-text3
# Markdown
cask install macdown

## Desktop
# Proper screen ligthing
cask install flux
# QuickLook plugins
cask install qlcolorcode qlstephen qlmarkdown quicklook-json betterzipql suspicious-package
# Window management
cask install spectacle

## Media
# Video player
cask install vlc
# PDF reader
cask install skim
# Picture viewer
cask install xee22
# Comic reader
cask install simple-comic
# Sonos music manager
cask install sonos
# Soundcloud client (yes, that's the correct spelling)
cask install soundcleod
# Adobe Flash
cask install flash
# Music player - install vox from App Store instead

## Work
# Screen recording
cask install screenflow
# Note taking
cask install evernote
# VMware View
cask install vmware-horizon-view-client

## Social
# Skype
cask install skype

## Storage
# Online storage
cask install dropbox
cask install google-drive
# Compression
cask install keka

## Games
# Steam client - now possible to stream games from the gaming rig to the Mac!
cask install steam
